    "body": "## Problem\r\n\r\nIf `UV_PROCESS_DETACHED` is not set when using `uv_spawn`, which is called by `vim.system`, the child process does not get its own process group and it therefore becomes impossible to kill its descendants, resulting in #39552.\r\n\r\n## Solution\r\n\r\nThis PR simply makes `vim.system` mimic the internal functions called by `jobstart` (`libuv_proc_spawn` and `os_proc_tree_kill`). ",
    "closed_at": null,
